Video: Heila-puppy is the latest dog reinforcement from Customs - puppy becomes the first explosive dog
A black Labrador puppy sniffs vigorously at five similar boxes lined up on the ground at Helsinki Airport.
It won't be long before it sits resolutely next to the middle box.
Customs inspector Lassi Suntio rewards his Heila dog for playing with his favorite toy.
